English Question:
If 3 be the one of the roots of x^{2} - kx + 2 = 0, then-
 i. another root will be \frac{2}{3}
 ii. the value of k will be \frac{11}{3}
 iii. discriminant of the equation will be 7
 Which one is correct?

Bengali Question:
